description:
職責
迎接客人並協助客人上落車並將客人送到目的地;
為客人打開豪華轎車車門，為有特別需要人士如長者提供幫忙;
幫助客人裝卸行李，並將行李帶入機場和酒店;
日常清潔與維護維修保養及牌照繢期;
定期檢查車輪狀況，節約燃油，保障行車安全;
記錄上下客信息和提交日報。
Job responsibilites

Greet and drive guest to destinations;
Provide special assistance to guests with special needs such as the elderly;
Assist Guests load and unload luggage when embarking and disembarking in airport and hotel;
Daily cleaning and maintenance;
Ensuring driving safety;
Create daily driving logs.
入職要求

持有有效駕駛執照(1號);
具至少3年相關經驗, 曾從事旅遊業者優先考慮;
中五程度以上;
良好英語及普通話能力;
可輪班工作。

Requirements

Hold valid Driving License No.1;
Not less than 3 years relevant experience; worked in travel industry is an advantage;
Completion of Secondary 5;
Good at English and Putonghua;
Can work on shift.
